{"is_ragtime":true,"metadata":{"team_id":"T311","run_id":"eel","topic_id":"1119","request_id":"1119","narrative_id":"1119"},"responses":[{"citations":{"3c29e522-5c23-4b52-88ad-d09ae0ea9bf4_378764971":0.08642994207121497},"text":"Avon, for instance, shifted towards an MLM model, focusing on recruiting salespeople rather than direct sales, which led to a decline in revenue and stock value."},{"citations":{"3c29e522-5c23-4b52-88ad-d09ae0ea9bf4_378764971":0.08642994207121497},"text":"Tupperware also faced similar challenges, becoming a \"walking dinosaur\" in the industry."},{"citations":{"a874023e-781f-4440-9c1e-f8647ce2dc46_713297395":0.11707981503686896},"text":"Educational Development Corporation (EDUC), for example, saw an increase in sales as home-based learning became more prevalent, and unemployment led more people to seek part-time work as sales consultants."},{"citations":{"3c29e522-5c23-4b52-88ad-d09ae0ea9bf4_378764971":0.08642994207121497},"text":"The model relies heavily on recruitment, and the majority of profits are concentrated among the top 1% of participants."},{"citations":{"3c29e522-5c23-4b52-88ad-d09ae0ea9bf4_378764971":0.09497965023911728},"text":"This structure has led to criticism and accusations of being akin to pyramid schemes."},{"citations":{"3c29e522-5c23-4b52-88ad-d09ae0ea9bf4_378764971":0.08642994207121497},"text":"However, the high churn rates and low success rates for most participants highlight the risks involved."}],"answer":[{"citations":{"3c29e522-5c23-4b52-88ad-d09ae0ea9bf4_378764971":0.08642994207121497},"text":"Avon, for instance, shifted towards an MLM model, focusing on recruiting salespeople rather than direct sales, which led to a decline in revenue and stock value."},{"citations":{"3c29e522-5c23-4b52-88ad-d09ae0ea9bf4_378764971":0.08642994207121497},"text":"Tupperware also faced similar challenges, becoming a \"walking dinosaur\" in the industry."},{"citations":{"a874023e-781f-4440-9c1e-f8647ce2dc46_713297395":0.1170798150368